The Glenn Beck Radio Show JULY-23-2014 WED


The Glenn Beck Program

  The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET





        
      
      Chris McDaniel Updates His Fight vs. Thad Cochran 

                 and Sen. Rand Paul Answers Tough Questions 7/23/14


Wednesday, July 23, 2014 10:44 AM


Glenn discusses how to carry on a conversation with the left about the border,

 the U.S. government setting up Israel and one commentator's
    unapologetic defense of one man's opinion. 

Chris McDaniel joins Glenn to discuss his battle with Senator Thad Cochran 
    and Senator Rand Paul addresses why so many are upset with him.

              That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!

The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET
